anch office it offers vstac os a software that forms a virtual hypersan to unite and share storage and compute resources across various nodes and virtual machines to enable global hyperconvergence acuity a software platform that simplifies workload management with policybased management engine and compr pivot inc provides hyperconverged infrastructure solutions for enterprise it in the united states and internationally the company’s hyperconverged platforms are used for highperformance workloads in dataintensive environments such as virtual desktop infrastructure video surveillance disaster recovery server virtualization big data data center consolidation and remote and branch office it offers vstac os a software that forms a virtual hypersan to unite and share storage and compute resources across various nodes and virtual machines to enable global hyperconvergence acuity a software platform that simplifies workload management with policybased management engine and comprehensive data services global hyperconverged infrastructure hci platforms that allow to pool various resources to compute memory and storage at scale to deliver hci system in the market and globally hyperconverged security platforms that are designed to ensure that various critical video surveillance streams are stored and protected the company also provides professional services technical support and online support portal it offers its products through distributors and resellers in the united states canada europe the middle east africa latin american caribbean and the asia pacific the company has a strategic partnership with gotham technology group pivot inc was founded in  and is based in austin texas with additional offices in derby united kingdom seoul korea dubai united arab emirates and singapore it also has a development center in spring texas detailed description  west sixth streetsuite austin tx united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwpivotcom key executives for pivot inc mr h ronald nash chairman and chief executive officer mr bill galloway founder chief technology officer and vice president mr wilbur g stover jr chief financial officer and vice president age  mr james j lerner chief operating officer and vice president age  mr bruce milne chief marketing officer and vice president compensation as of fiscal year  pivot inc key developments pivot names carlo garbagnati as vice president of engineering may   pivot announced carlo garbagnati as vice president of engineering garbagnati will be responsible for leading the development efforts of company’s entire solution portfolio and driving roadmap execution to sustain the company’s exponential growth and evolution within the market garbagnati was most recently the vice president of hyperconverged and nas engineering at hitachi where he led hundreds of engineers on multiple projects for enterpriseclass storage solutions big data and analytics and hyperconverged and softwaredefined infrastructures he has experience as a senior research and development leader in startups as well as large multinational companies with a deep focus on softwaredefined storage and hyperconverged infrastructure technologies prior to hitachi garbagnati led the engineering efforts at bluearc garbagnati has also held senior leadership positions at several emerging technology companies including quantum meridian parallan and olivetti pivot announces the release of acuity apr   pivot announced the release of acuity the industry’s first priorityaware hci software platform that enables it to confidently consolidate multiple mixedapplication workloads onto a single infrastructure while also delivering breakthrough performance pivot’s new acuity software platform delivers greater performance scale and efficiency across a wider range of applications to overcome these limitations acuity simplifies workload management with pivot’s fifthgeneration policybased management engine and comprehensive data services as a priorityaware software platform acuity intelligently and automatically applies resources to missioncritical applications for guaranteed performance and predictable results acuity’s advanced policybased management engine has been optimized to make the most efficient use of nvme pcie flash to deliver six times the performance of conventional hci solutions this means it can improve response times for databases enterprise applications business analytics and vdi acuity also delivers increased density enabling it to run two to three times more virtual machines per hci node resulting in a smaller datacenter footprint and significant reductions in opex and capex acuity is architected for performance fully leveraging the acceleration of ultralowlatency nvme pcie flash with nvme pcie flash data path performance under control of pivot’s advanced policybased quality of service qos engine organizations can consolidate performance and latencysensitive applications onto hci with flash that is  faster than sata ssd and  faster than sas ssd pivot and intelligent security systems announces original equipment manufacturer agreement apr   pivot announced a strategic original equipment manufacturer relationship with intelligent security systems iss under the agreement iss will license the pivot hyperconverged infrastructure hci platform and integrate it with iss video management software vms to supply more robust security intelligence and video storage options to customers the addition of pivot hci solutions which are optimized for the writeintensive demands of video surveillance workloads is a natural complement to iss video surveillance technologies the iss framework manages and monitors an unlimited number of cameras and devices applies intelligent video analytics and integrates a variety of disparate systems into one centralized interface this approach allows users to leverage video data to achieve new levels of security intelligence and situational awareness through its partnership with pivot iss will provide tailor made solutions as well as enterpriseclass video analytics in a scalable architecture that is easy to deploy and simple to manage the platforms architecture is optimized for ip video to prevent video loss and image quality degradation pivots highly available softwaredefined storage technology ensures previously recorded video remains accessible even if entire appliances go offline this extreme resiliency ensures critical data is protected and available for security liability business intelligence and risk management requirements additionally systems can easily be expanded as needs grow without disrupting operations while other applications such as access control visitor management and video analytics can be consolidated on the pivot system to further reduce costs and improve reliability similar private companies by industry company name region  beyond inc united states  south networks inc united states  retail markets llc united states ality inc united states d digital corp united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region lawyers committee for civil rights under law united states nyc inc united states bertelsmann ag europe the advertising council inc united states rush university united states sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company profile documentation will be required to contact pivot inc please v